headline: 4 Things To Consider Ahead Of The June 2025 Federal Reserve Meeting
summary: Markets expect steady Fed rates amid soft jobs and inflation, with tariffs shifting consumer trends and risks rising. See why investors eye Fed cuts in 2025.
